T02TD2416E:35a-1: sa ha dza aa nanta sva bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02TD2416E:35a-3: lhan cig skyes pa'i rang bzhin zhes bya ba /
T02TD2416E:35a-4: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2416E:35a-5: 'khor lo rna rgyan mgul rgyan gdu bu dang //
T02TD2416E:35a-6: ska rags khyod la bzang zhing rab tu mdzes //
T02TD2416E:35a-7: bo la kakko la myos ngo mtshar tshe ;
T02TD2416E:35a-8: / skad cig gcig la he ru ka dpal dgyes //
T02TD2416E:35a-9: kye ho rtsa lag 'di la bdag yid dga' //

T02TD2416E:35a-12: rnal 'byor ma kye 'di la bdag yid dga' //
T02TD2416E:35a-13: 'jigs byed dus mtshan zhabs kyi 'og tu mnan //
T02TD2416E:35a-14: nam mkha'i mthar thug he dang h'um sgra spro //
T02TD2416E:35a-15: phyogs bcur chang gis myas pa yi //
T02TD2416E:35a-17: kye ma dpa' bo rnal 'byor med //
T02TD2416E:35a-18: stong pa dang ni snying rje'i rang bzhin la //
T02TD2416E:35a-19: dngos dang dngos med gnyis ka med //
T02TD2416E:35a-20: pra phab gzugs bzhin mkha' la snod //
T02TD2416E:35a-21: kye ho rnal 'byor ma dang yum lnga'i grong //
T02TD2416E:35a-22: a'a li dang ni k'a li nyi ma rnams //
T02TD2416E:35a-23: mad pa rmongs pa rnams kyang gti mug che //
T02TD2416E:35a-24: a'a li rnams dang k'a li nyi zla dag / med la shes min phyugs 'dra the tshom med //
T02TD2416E:35a-25: dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma rnam sbyor ba yis //
